---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout
  title="Privacy Policy — ShipNode"
  description="ShipNode is an open-source CLI that does not collect personal data, track usage, or store logs on ShipNode servers."
>
  <main class="page" id="main-content">
    <div class="container">
      <h1>Privacy policy</h1>
      <p class="lead">ShipNode does not collect personal data.</p>
      <p>This is an open-source CLI tool. It runs on your machine and your server. We do not track usage, store logs on our servers, or share any information with third parties.</p>
      <p>The only network requests ShipNode makes are:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>To your own server over SSH</li>
        <li>To GitHub (optional, for CI/CD workflow generation)</li>
        <li>To Let's Encrypt (handled by Caddy on your server)</li>
      </ul>
      <p>If you have questions, open an issue on <a href="https://github.com/devalade/shipnode" target="_blank" rel="noopener">GitHub</a>.</p>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>

<style>
  .page {
    padding: 8rem var(--space-xl) var(--space-4xl);
  }
  .container {
    max-width: 640px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }
  h1 {
    font-size: clamp(1.75rem, 4vw, 2.5rem);
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: -0.03em;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
    text-wrap: balance;
  }
  .lead {
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-xl);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }
  p, ul {
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
  }
  ul { padding-left: 1.25rem; }
  li { margin-bottom: var(--space-xs); }
  a { color: var(--accent-hover); text-decoration: underline; text-underline-offset: 3px; }
  a:hover { color: var(--text-primary); }
</style>
